@policy(id="dev-testing", version="1.0"):
  @meta(created="2026-01-15", updated="2026-01-28"):
    Description: Development and testing policy - relaxed requirements
    Owner: Development Team
    Environment: staging, development

  @requires(attestation="optional", min-signatures=1):
    Development bundles MAY skip Rekor transparency log
    At least 1 signature recommended but not enforced

    @trusted-keys:
      - dev-signing-key
      - test-signing-key

  @requires(sbom="optional"):
    SBOM recommended but not required for development builds
    CVE scanning recommended (informational only)

  @requires(registry-allowlist):
    @allowed:
      - docker.io
      - ghcr.io
      - localhost:5000
      - "*"

    @blocked:
      - NONE

    Rationale: Development allows any registry for testing

  @requires(build-attestation="optional"):
    Build provenance optional for dev builds
    Local builds allowed

  @audit(log="/var/log/ct/dev-policy.log"):
    Minimal logging for development:
    - Bundle hash
    - Timestamp
    - Pass/fail result

  @attestation(policy-signature):
    signed-by: dev-admin-key
    signature: ed25519:1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1e2f3a4b5c6d7e8f9a0b1c2d3e4f5a6b7c8d9e0f1a2b
    timestamp: 2026-01-28T10:15:00Z
@end
